    "comparability_notes": "EPD uses PCR 2019:14 v1.3.4 (2024-04-30) and EN 15804+A2:2019. Scope is cradle to gate A1-A3 with options A4, A5, C1-C4 and D. A1, A2, A3 are not reported separately — only the A1-A3 aggregate is declared. The product covers multiple production sites across Melbourne Metro (VIC): Laverton, Truganina, Footscray, Epping, Keilor, Preston, Oaklands Junction, Melbourne Airport, Bayswater, Springvale, Lyndhurst, Seaford, Pakenham, Hastings, Rosebud — grouped under a single dataset. Reference year is 2022 for plant data and 2025 for mix/materials data. B1–B7 modules are not declared (deemed not applicable). ECOPact is Holcim's low-carbon concrete range."
